### ==================== AUTHENTICATION ====================

### Login (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "clubCode": "CLUB-001",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "isAdmin": true
}

### Login (Member)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "membershipId": "MEM-12345",
  "sequenceNumber": "01",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "isAdmin": false
}

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "phoneNumber": "01000000000"
}


### ==================== SPORTS ====================

### Get Sports Screen
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sports/screen?sportId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Sports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Upcoming Classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sports/classes?sportId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Sport Class (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sports/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning Yoga Session",
  "description": "Relaxing morning yoga session for all levels.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/yoga.jpg",
  "sportId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-05-01T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-05-01T09:00:00Z",
  "location": "Main Hall",
  "maxParticipants": 20,
  "price": 50.0,
  "type": "Regular"
}

### Book a Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sports/classes/1/book
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sports/my-bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== EVENTS ====================

### Get Featured Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/featured
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Upcoming Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Event By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Event (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Festival",
  "description": "Biggest summer festival in the club with many activities.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/festival.jpg",
  "startDate": "2026-07-15T18:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-07-15T23:00:00Z",
  "location": "Club Garden",
  "price": 150.0,
  "isFeatured": true,
  "capacity": 500
}


### ==================== SERVICES ====================

### Get Quick Services
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/services/quick
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Services
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Service (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spa & Massage",
  "description": "Full body massage and spa treatment.",
  "icon": "spa-icon",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/spa.jpg",
  "price": 300.0,
  "isQuickService": false
}


### ==================== NOTIFICATIONS ====================

### Get My Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Unread Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Notification (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "System Update",
  "message": "We have updated the club app! Enjoy the new features.",
  "userId": null, 
  "type": "System"
}

### Mark All As Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== BANNERS ====================

### Get All Banners
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Banner (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Special Discount",
  "description": "Get 20% off on all spa services this weekend!",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/banner.jpg",
  "linkUrl": "/services/spa",
  "isActive": true
}
